  "title": "IT Executive / IT Network & System Support ( Woodalnds )Junior 1-2 years exp",
  "description": "<p>1. IT Infrastructure Support </p><p>· Maintain and troubleshoot hardware (PCs, printers, barcode scanners, etc.) </p><p>· Support network infrastructure: LAN/WAN, switches, routers, Wi-Fi </p><p>· Ensure servers and data storage are running smoothly (file servers, domain controllers) </p><p>2. System Administration </p><p>· Manage user accounts, email, Active Directory, file permissions </p><p>· Monitor IT security (antivirus, firewalls, data protection policies) </p><p>· Perform regular backups and ensure disaster recovery plans are in place </p><p>3. Manufacturing/Production System Support </p><p>· Provide technical support for MES (Manufacturing Execution Systems), ERP, or factory-specific systems </p><p>Requirement </p><p>· Diploma or Degree in Information Technology, Computer Science, Engineering, or related field </p><p>· 1–3 years of experience in IT support, networking, or systems administration </p><p>Good Pay + Good allowance + Good Bonus </p><p>Interested candidates please send an updated Resume / CV in Ms Word format to lilian@recruitflash.com or WhatsApp’s your resume to 98332779 ( no Calls) </p><p>Consultant in-charge : Quah Li Lian (Lilian) ( Registration No: R1983286 ) </p>",
